  "detailed_description": "<h1>GREAT CYBERPUNK GAME BY OUR FRIENDS</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/13ab1bd725801633b5e4036cd40f6f7b.avif?t=1771983713\" width=500 height=117 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/442a550a23af25bd5036bcda652e4e97.avif?t=1771983713\" width=500 height=117 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/bab40e33e8cc9f7c45573afa068f0dcc.avif?t=1771983713\" width=600 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Meta Ghost: Breaking Show</strong> is a <i>3D roguelite hack-and-slash action</i> game. Built on the foundation of \"cyberpunk\" culture, the game provides a thrilling and fast-paced combat experience while telling a profound cyberpunk story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/e97618e3efb9b36e463c865c4cf9ef9c.avif?t=1771983713\" width=600 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/2e47ed2a3ca36ec81f96398374361117.poster.avif?t=1771983713\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/2e47ed2a3ca36ec81f96398374361117.webm?t=1771983713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/2e47ed2a3ca36ec81f96398374361117.mp4?t=1771983713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as one “breaker” (or several) in Breaking Show, battling intelligent machines with cybernetic enhancements and state-of-the-art weapons provided by the organizers in the future city of \"Aeropolis.\" With each defeat or victory, you will gradually uncover the secrets of \"the soul\" and the outcome it desires...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/25f24dabe54f6a3aadcb5d19b1355593.avif?t=1771983713\" width=600 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/2f07e330d4c18095ca9d09d82b021468.poster.avif?t=1771983713\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/2f07e330d4c18095ca9d09d82b021468.webm?t=1771983713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/2f07e330d4c18095ca9d09d82b021468.mp4?t=1771983713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a Breaking Show participant with your own personal channel, you must get used to fighting on live broadcasts. Not only do you need to defeat every mechanical opponent in front of you, but you also need to strive for visually stunning performances to please event sponsors and viewers eagerly anticipating your cool moves. Their likes and dislikes will either aid or hinder you on the field.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/9df5d515e9c84ceaa443c17ef140027d.avif?t=1771983713\" width=600 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/94e2748170bb8ee275199123f3842103.poster.avif?t=1771983713\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/94e2748170bb8ee275199123f3842103.webm?t=1771983713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/94e2748170bb8ee275199123f3842103.mp4?t=1771983713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combining elements of \"glitch art,\" \"street art,\" \"pop art,\" and other trendsetting styles creates a unique \"cyber graffiti style\" with a cutting-edge feel and visual impact.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/6ab9b55f1f577a6b95ad4fa6cb7a5ddd.avif?t=1771983713\" width=600 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/1304e1427f6798ef0f50c0ada79df4f3.poster.avif?t=1771983713\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/1304e1427f6798ef0f50c0ada79df4f3.webm?t=1771983713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/1304e1427f6798ef0f50c0ada79df4f3.mp4?t=1771983713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/ca2726a16d66264585fc52c7035c6af9.poster.avif?t=1771983713\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/ca2726a16d66264585fc52c7035c6af9.webm?t=1771983713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/ca2726a16d66264585fc52c7035c6af9.mp4?t=1771983713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through the participant's lounge modification pod, you can enhance and modify your cybernetic enhancements and weapons, creating a dangerous and diverse fighting style. From event organizers to sponsors, you will have access to a vast array of freely combinable and customizable drivers to equip your cybernetic enhancements with special abilities, making you unbeatable on the field. The relics of other eliminated contestants left on the field will also be a major asset, allowing you to break through with their unfulfilled beliefs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/4b0dae71af3939fa028f7434a1758af3.avif?t=1771983713\" width=600 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/4f43a26cabba9c60d44ff1d3a262cfdb.poster.avif?t=1771983713\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/4f43a26cabba9c60d44ff1d3a262cfdb.webm?t=1771983713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/4f43a26cabba9c60d44ff1d3a262cfdb.mp4?t=1771983713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/9e22f355604d9d200d10f260ccc09c9c.poster.avif?t=1771983713\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/9e22f355604d9d200d10f260ccc09c9c.webm?t=1771983713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/9e22f355604d9d200d10f260ccc09c9c.mp4?t=1771983713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Breaking Show offers a range of combat styles to suit your preferences, whether you prefer hit-and-run tactics, head-on defense and counterattacks, or precise finesse. The Breakers in the lounge are a diverse group with unique fighting styles, providing a variety of experiences and event performances. Intelligent machines, poised to replace soldiers, agents, and bodyguards, are also preparing for the competition with flexible cooperation, adding to the already diverse lineup and ensuring that every contestant attempting to climb to the top will be successfully blocked.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/a98829733bca480d833009867d0b40ac.avif?t=1771983713\" width=600 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/faa47daef205b58fdde5a40d21825215.poster.avif?t=1771983713\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/faa47daef205b58fdde5a40d21825215.webm?t=1771983713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/faa47daef205b58fdde5a40d21825215.mp4?t=1771983713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the venue for Breaking Show, the temporarily closed-off streets may appear normal, but be sure to watch every step you take, even on drainage grates or manhole covers - they could become deadly traps at any moment. Of course, this is only if you can keep your focus while taking down every mechanical opponent in front of you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/bab40e33e8cc9f7c45573afa068f0dcc.avif?t=1771983713\" width=600 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/fdddf0bf65ffbdf743958f2642a7259f.poster.avif?t=1771983713\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/fdddf0bf65ffbdf743958f2642a7259f.webm?t=1771983713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/fdddf0bf65ffbdf743958f2642a7259f.mp4?t=1771983713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So, are you ready to make a name for yourself as a participant in the new season? After all, \"the soul\" is watching and eagerly anticipating your arrival.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/13ab1bd725801633b5e4036cd40f6f7b.avif?t=1771983713\" width=500 height=117 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/442a550a23af25bd5036bcda652e4e97.avif?t=1771983713\" width=500 height=117 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/bab40e33e8cc9f7c45573afa068f0dcc.avif?t=1771983713\" width=600 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Meta Ghost: Breaking Show</strong> is a <i>3D roguelite hack-and-slash action</i> game. Built on the foundation of \"cyberpunk\" culture, the game provides a thrilling and fast-paced combat experience while telling a profound cyberpunk story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/e97618e3efb9b36e463c865c4cf9ef9c.avif?t=1771983713\" width=600 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/2e47ed2a3ca36ec81f96398374361117.poster.avif?t=1771983713\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/2e47ed2a3ca36ec81f96398374361117.webm?t=1771983713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507980/extras/2e47ed2a3ca3